  <entry>
    <title>Python-在类方法中传递类对象</title>
    <link href="/2022/05/11/Python-%E5%9C%A8%E7%B1%BB%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%92%E7%B1%BB%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1/"/>
    <url>/2022/05/11/Python-%E5%9C%A8%E7%B1%BB%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%92%E7%B1%BB%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言:"></a>前言:</h2><ul><li>python的语法非常灵活</li><li>Python可以直接将一个类对象当做参数传递给函数（方法）而不需要任何说明</li><li>比较两数的大小只需将两数相减</li></ul><h2 id="问题："><a href="#问题：" class="headerlink" title="问题："></a>问题：</h2><blockquote><p>定义一个学生类，学生具备 stuID、stuName 与 stuAge 属性，还具备一个比较年龄的方法。</p></blockquote><h2 id="思路："><a href="#思路：" class="headerlink" title="思路："></a>思路：</h2><ul><li>前半句很好解决，直接定义一个类即可</li><li>后半句要求在方法中比较年龄，故将类对象作为参数传递给类方法即可，比较则用两数相减的方式</li></ul><h2 id="代码实现"><a href="#代码实现" class="headerlink" title="代码实现:"></a>代码实现:</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs python"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Student</span>(<span class="hljs-title class_ inherited__">object</span>): <span class="hljs-comment"># 学生类</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">__init__</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self, ID, name, age</span>) -&gt; <span class="hljs-literal">None</span>:<br>        self.ID = ID<br>        self.name = name<br>        self.age = age<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">pass</span><br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">def</span> <span class="hljs-title function_">ageCompare</span>(<span class="hljs-params">self, stu_object</span>) -&gt; <span class="hljs-built_in">int</span>: <span class="hljs-comment"># 比较方法</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> self.age - stu_object.age<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="运行结果："><a href="#运行结果：" class="headerlink" title="运行结果："></a>运行结果：</h2><img src="/2022/05/11/Python-%E5%9C%A8%E7%B1%BB%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%E4%B8%AD%E4%BC%A0%E9%80%92%E7%B1%BB%E5%AF%B9%E8%B1%A1/%E8%BF%90%E8%A1%8C%E7%BB%93%E6%9E%9C.png" class="" title="运行结果">]]></content>
    
    
